# UI/UX Standards

## Mobile-first

- No hover-only controls (`opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100`). Use always-visible actions or a kebab/dropdown menu.
- Header action rows: `flex flex-wrap gap-2`
- Dense tables: card/stack layout below `md` breakpoint
- Dialog forms: `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4` not fixed `grid-cols-4`

## Touch targets

- Minimum interactive size ~44px on mobile (`h-10`, `min-h-10`)
- Spacing between adjacent actions: `gap-2` minimum

## Dialogs

- Max width: `max-w-lg` default, `max-w-4xl` for editors
- Height: `max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto` on small screens

## Admin shell

- Sidebar collapses to drawer on mobile (Sheet)
- Page titles + primary action in sticky header with wrap
